1. *Svemiru* nema kraja. (There is no end to *space*.)
2. *Svemir* je fascinantan. (*Space* is fascinating.)
3. Planete se kreću po *svemiru*. (Planets move through *space*.)
4. *Svemirska* letelica je lansirana u orbitu. (*Spacecraft* was launched into orbit.)
5. Astronauti su proveli godine u istraživanju *svemira*. (Astronauts spent years exploring *space*.)
6. *Svemirska* stanica orbitira oko Zemlje. (*Space* station orbits around the Earth.)
7. Naučnici pokušavaju da prouče tajne *svemira*. (Scientists are trying to study the secrets of *space*.)
8. *Svemirski* programi su skupi ali važni. (*Space* programs are expensive but important.)
9. Zvezde sijaju na nebu, visoko u *svemiru*. (Stars shine in the sky, high up in *space*.)
10. Sateliti nam omogućavaju komunikaciju preko *svemira*. (Satellites enable communication through *space*.)

(Note: The word "svemiru" appears in sentence 1, and variations of the word "svemir" appear in sentences 2, 3, 6, 7, 8, and 9. The word "svemirska" appears in sentences 4, 6, and 8, while the word "svemirski" appears in sentence 8. The translations are provided in parentheses after each sentence.)